Details
___________________________________________________________________________________

Natural beauty Aliyah for Genesis 3 Female comes with custom sculpted head, body, nipple and nail morphs, and a conforming set of fiberhair eyebrows.
But don't be deceived by her sweet innocent looks, Aliyah also has a dark side. Her alter-ego comes with a full vampire mat, optional bloody mouth and teeth.
Included as an added bonus are a set of conforming right and left vampire bites that can be used on any of your G3F/G3M victims. These have fresh and old bite materials for Iray and 3Delight.

Using the base G3F UVs, Aliyah only requires the free Genesis 3 Starter Essentials to work.

She has an additional seven eye colour options, five nail colours and five makeups. (Each of which comes with a painted brows and a no-brows texture option).
Both regular and vampire mats come complete with genital materials.
Her skin mats are optimised for both Iray and 3Delight renders.
Add her to your runtime and let your imagination run wild.
